Table of Ecommerce
--------------------------
User 
|---id 
|---password 
|---last_login 
|---is_superuser 
|---username
|---first_name 
|---last_name
|---email 
|---is_staff 	
|---is_active 
|---date_joined	

User Profile
|---id
|---user_id 
|---username
|---full_name
|---address_1
|---address_2
|---city 
|---postcode
|---country 
|---phone 
|---created_at
|---updated_at

Category
|---id
|---title
|---created _at
|---updated_at	

Product
|---id
|---mainimage
|---name
|---category_id
|---short_des 
|---long_des 
|---price 
|---old_price 
|---created_at
|---updated_at

Cart
|---id
|---user_id
|---product_id
|---quantity
|---purchased
|---created_at
|---updated_at	

Order
|---id
|---cart_items
|---user_id
|---ordered(def:False)
|---paymenId(transaction_id)
|---orderId

BillingAddress
|---id
|---user_id
|---address
|---zipcode
|---city 
|---country
|---created_at
|---updated_at	


